    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.97)) * wp.exp((tmp + 0.68 + v1 + 0.68)))
    v1 = wp.cos(((v1 + 1.00 / v0 + 1.00) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.41)))
    v0 = (wp.sin(v2) / wp.sin((v1 + 0.16 * v1 + 0.51)))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.74) + 0.27) - v2)
    data[tid] = v0
